<item>
            <title>[DATACMNS-407] Incorrect prev and next links when using paging and sorting</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/DATACMNS-407</link>
                <project id="10510" key="DATACMNS">Spring Data Commons</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I have a Spring MVC web application which uses PagedResourcesAssembler to introduce paging metadata. When you request the service by providing both paging and sorting parameters the &lt;tt&gt;next&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;prev&lt;/tt&gt; links are wrong - they duplicate the sorting parameter.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;When I investigated the issue I found that in &lt;tt&gt;HateoasSortHandlerMethodArgumentResolver&lt;/tt&gt; the query parameters are built with &lt;tt&gt;builder.queryParam(&#8230;)&lt;/tt&gt; instead of &lt;tt&gt;builder.replaceQueryParam(&#8230;)&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
